Johnnie Morris (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johnnie_Morris_(actor) 0 Phillip Morris (born April 4, 1959) is an American film, television and voice actor. He played Jackie Chiles in the NBC sitcom Seinfeld, John Jones in The CW superhero drama Smallville, Delroy Jones in Love That Girl! and voiced Doc Saturday in The Secret Saturdays.
